These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-8-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, january
There are 2 different nationalities: british, dutch
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, musical
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, taxi
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, iris
1. the person who growszinnia is on the far right##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
4. the person who growsiris is not to the right of the person who growszinnia##8
5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
6. the british is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |
| Birthday    | january   | october        |
| Nationality   | british    | dutch |
| Movie-Genre     | musical  | satire       |
| Transport     | roller   | taxi         |
| Flower   | iris | zinnia      |

