.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-8-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, havana
2 different games are played: whist, go
There are 2 different favourite colors: black, blue
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, german
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, juice
1. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
2. the person who likes blue is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes blue is not to the right of the german##8
4. the person playing go is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Cigar         | baccarat   | havana |
| Game   | go  | whist     |
| Color   | black  | blue        |
| Nationality           | indonesian     | german       |
| Beverage         | mirinda | juice     |

