.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-8-3::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, begonia
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, lemonade
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, architect
There 2 different types of food: cherry, avocado
1. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
2. the project-manager is not to the right of the person who growsmarigold##8
3. the project-manager is on the left or right of the person eating avocado##3
4. the person eating cherry is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |
| Transport         | bike  | helicopter |
| Flower   | begonia | marigold   |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | mirinda     |
| Job   | architect | project-manager     |
| Food           | avocado   | cherry      |

